*What is Poseur?*

- A _simple_ presentation viewer
- Written in *Python* using *pyglet*
- Free and open source
- Supports unicode: זרו ֶ״ֵ


*Some features*

- Write presentations in plain text
- Recognizes Markdown-syntax (not yet complete, though)


