*Text format*

- Use `*this*` to write *bold*
- Use `_this_` to write _italic_
- Use double linefeeds for next slide...


*Future features*

- Animation support
- Dual monitor support
- PNG/JPEG support
- AVI/movie support
- SVG/3D support
- Webcam support (for recording your sessions)
- ... and a lot more!
